text: (WAM) Number of Rulers, Crown Princes and Sheikhs attend Al Nahyan wedding ceremony at Emirates Palace A number of Supreme Council Members, Their Highnesses Rulers of Emirates, Crown Princes and Sheikhs, attended the wedding ceremony of Al Nahyan family held at Emirates Palace, Abu Dhabi, on Saturday. The reception was hosted by Sheikh Khalifa bin Hamdan Al Nahyan on the occasion of the wedding of his son, Sheikh Dhyiab, to the daughter of Sheikh Nahyan bin Mubarak Al Nahyan, Minister of Culture and Knowledge Development. The event was attended by Sheikh Humaid bin Rashid Al Nuaimi, Supreme Council Member and Ruler of Ajman; Sheikh Hamad bin Mohammed Al Sharqi, Supreme Council Member and Ruler of Fujairah; Sheikh Saud bin Rashid Al Mualla, Supreme Council Member and Ruler of Umm Al Qaiwain; Sheikh Saud bin Saqr Al Qasimi, Supreme Council Member and Ruler of Ras Khaimah; Sheikh Sultan bin Zayed Al Nahyan, the President's Representative, Sheikh Hamdan bin Mohammed bin Rashid Al Maktoum, Crown Prince of Dubai; Sheikh Hamdan bin Rashid Al Maktoum, Deputy Ruler of Dubai and UAE Minister of Finance, Sheikh Ammar bin Humaid Al Nuaimi, Crown Prince of Ajman, Sheikh Rashid bin Saud bin Rashid Al Mu'alla, Crown Prince of Umm Al Qaiwain; Sheikh Mohammed bin Saud bin Saqr Al Qasimi, Crown Prince of Ras al- Khaimah; and Sheikh Tahnoun bin Mohammed Al Nahyan, Ruler's Representative in the Eastern Region. (@_nahyaniah) on Feb 18, 2017 at 4:21am PST Among others present were Sheikh Saif bin Mohammed Al Nahyan, Sheikh Suroor bin Mohammed Al Nahyan; Sheikh Hazza bin Zayed Al Nahyan, Deputy Chairman of the Executive Council of the Emirate of Abu Dhabi; Sheikh Nahyan bin Zayed Al Nahyan, Chairman of the Board of Trustees of Zayed bin Sultan Al Nahyan Charitable and Humanitarian Foundation; Lt. General Sheikh Saif bin Zayed Al Nahyan, Deputy Prime Minister and Minister of Interior; Sheikh Mansour bin Zayed Al Nahyan, Deputy Prime Minister and Minister of Presidential Affairs; Sheikh Hamed bin Zayed Al Nahyan, Chief of the Abu Dhabi Crown Prince's; Sheikh Abdullah bin Zayed Al Nahyan, Minister of Foreign Affairs and International Cooperation; Sheikh Omar bin Zayed Al Nahyan, Deputy Chairman of the Board of Trustees of the Zayed bin Sultan Al Nahyan Charitable and Humanitarian Foundation; Sheikh Khalid bin Zayed Al Nahyan Chairman of the Board of Zayed Higher Organisation for Humanitarian Care & Special Needs; Sheikh Mohammed bin Khalifa Al Nahyan, Executive Council Member; Sheikh Mansour bin Mohammed bin Rashid Al Maktoum; Sheikh Sultan bin Hamdan Al Nahyan, Advisor to the UAE President; Dr Sheikh Saeed bin Mohammed Al Nahyan; H.H. Sheikh Nahyan bin Mubarak Al Nahyan, Minister of Culture and Knowledge Development, and Sheikh Sultan bin Tahnoun Al Nahyan, Member of the Executive Council. Also present were Sheikh Hazza bin Tahnoun, Under-Secretary of Ruler's Representative Court in Eastern Region, Brig. Sheikh Mohammed bin Tahnoun Al Nahyan, Director-General of the Security and Ports Affairs at Abu Dhabi Police, Sheikh Dhyiab bin Tahnoun Al Nahyan, Sheikh Khalifa bin Tahnoun bin Mohammed Al Nahyan, Director of The Martyrs' Families' Affairs Office at the Abu Dhabi Crown Prince's Court, Sheikh Rashid bin Humaid Al Nuaimi, Chairman of Ajman Municipality and Planning Department, a number of Sheikhs, ministers and dignitaries.
